### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Local API testing workflow
###
### The dev profile disables CSRF (see SecurityConfig), so requests below
### only need a session cookie — no X-XSRF-TOKEN header to wrangle.
###
### One-time per app restart:
###   1. Run the app:  `./mvnw spring-boot:run`  (with GOOGLE_OAUTH_*
###      env vars set; see README "Authentication" section).
###   2. In your browser, visit  http://localhost:8080/api/me  →  sign in
###      with Google.
###   3. Open browser DevTools → Application → Cookies → localhost:8080
###      and copy the value of the JSESSIONID cookie.
###   4. Paste it into  backend/requests/http-client.private.env.json
###      (copy from the .example file if you don't have it yet — the
###      .private.env.json file is gitignored).
###   5. In the JetBrains HTTP Client toolbar (top-right of this editor),
###      pick the "dev" environment, then click ▶ on any request.
###
### When the cookie expires (server restart, logout), repeat steps 2-4.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------

### Smoke check — health endpoint (public, no cookie needed)
GET {{host}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Current user (auth required) — confirms login worked
GET {{host}}/api/me
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Accept: application/json

###

### List all todos (default — same as ?status=all)
GET {{host}}/api/todos
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Accept: application/json

###

### List active todos
GET {{host}}/api/todos?status=active
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Accept: application/json

###

### List completed todos
GET {{host}}/api/todos?status=completed
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a todo (201 Created + Location header)
POST {{host}}/api/todos
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy almond milk"
}

###

### Get one todo by id
GET {{host}}/api/todos/1
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Accept: application/json

###

### PATCH — toggle completed
PATCH {{host}}/api/todos/1
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "completed": true
}

###

### PATCH — change title only
PATCH {{host}}/api/todos/2
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy oat milk"
}

###

### PATCH — both fields
PATCH {{host}}/api/todos/1
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Renew library books",
  "completed": false
}

###

### DELETE — 204 No Content
DELETE {{host}}/api/todos/1
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}

###

### Validation error — empty title -> 400 ProblemDetail with field errors
POST {{host}}/api/todos
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": ""
}

###

### Validation error — title over 255 chars -> 400
POST {{host}}/api/todos
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "{{$randomString 300}}"
}

###

### 404 — non-existent id -> 404 ProblemDetail
GET {{host}}/api/todos/999999
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 400 — invalid status filter value -> 400 ProblemDetail
GET {{host}}/api/todos?status=banana
Cookie: JSESSIONID={{JSESSIONID}}
Accept: application/json
